Patches							*patches-8.2*
-------

These patches were applied after the 8.1 release and are included in the 8.2
release.

Patch 8.1.0001
Problem:    The netrw plugin does not work.
Solution:   Make it accept version 8.x.
Files:      runtime/autoload/netrw.vim

